definitions.definition: A hydroxy quaternary ammonium compound with formula ( CH 3 ) 3 N CH 2 CH 2 OH X . It is an essential nutrient for cardiovascular and brain health and for cell membrane formation.

main_definition: ( organic chemistry ) A hydroxy quaternary ammonium compound with formula ( CH 3 ) 3 N CH 2 CH 2 OH X . It is an essential nutrient for cardiovascular and brain health and for cell membrane formation.
